<P>__{(calling)}
<D>__{come on out, phillips.}
<A>__{his voice echoes again and again. clay's answer is a shot. it cuts the branches above lednov's head.}
<B>__{close shot}
<A>__{lednov. he ducks lower, steadies his rifle.}
<C>__{lednov}
<P>__{(his voice echoing)}
<D>__{those horses down there they don't amount to much to me. look at the one with the bell.}
<B>__{long shot}
